casebody.data:
No. 10M38. In re Grand Jury Proceedings. 562 U.S. 979, 131 S. Ct. 441,

178 L. Ed. 2d 319,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8245. October 18, 2010.

Motion of Reporters Committee for Freedom of the Press for leave to intervene denied. Motion for leave to file a petition for writ of certiorari under seal with redacted copies for the public record granted.
